Violet Knights https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violet_Knights 0 Violet Knights (15 May 1894 – 13 June 1973) was an American silent film actress. Knights was born in Anacortes, Washington. She was signed in 1913 and starred in about 10 films between 1913 and 1914. She left acting and married and concentrated on raising a family becoming Violet MacKaye. She returned to acting 16 years later in The Cheyenne Kid in 1930 but her several minor roles following that were uncredited. She died in Newport Beach, aged 79.
